13
00:01:49,500 --> 00:01:51,583
<i>Ils se disputaient leur propre peau.</i>

14
00:01:52,750 --> 00:01:53,917
<i>Signor </i>Gucci ?

15
00:02:05,458 --> 00:02:14,583
LA SAGA GUCCI

16
00:02:27,542 --> 00:02:30,000
INSPIRÉ D'UNE HISTOIRE VRAIE

17
00:02:49,292 --> 00:02:50,583
