18
00:02:50,750 --> 00:02:51,750
Hé ! Allez.

19
00:03:42,542 --> 00:03:44,375
Parfaite ! Comme la mienne.

20
00:03:44,542 --> 00:03:46,750
Fernando Reggiani.

21
00:03:48,667 --> 00:03:49,500
Bonne fille.

22
00:03:49,667 --> 00:03:51,333
